\v 13 Zwanini lifakaze\x + 1.13; 4.1; 5.1; 7.16; 8.4; Jow. 1.2; Hos. 5.1.\x* endlini kaJakobe\x + Dute. 8.19; Neh. 9.34; Hlab. 50.7; 81.8.\x*, itsho iNkosi uJehova uNkulunkulu wamabandla\x + Hlab. 80.7,14; Amos 4.13; 5.14-16; 5.27; 6.8,14.\x*,
