\v 15 Ngizatshaya\x + 6.11.\x* indlu yebusika\x + Jer. 36.22.\x* kanye lendlu yehlobo\x + Hlu. 3.20.\x*, lezindlu zempondo zendlovu zizabhubha\x + 1 Kho. 22.39; Hlab. 45.8.\x*, lezindlu ezinkulu ziphele; itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*.
